<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/138.0.0.0 YaBrowser/25.8.0.0 Safari/537.36" version="29.0.3"> <diagram name="Страница-1" id="DJCuTXIjLPYNrIznjRAE"> <mxGraphModel dx="1828" dy="2125" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{"data":"@startuml Smart Cards ER Diagram

!define PRIMARY_KEY(x) <b><color:red>x</color></b>
!define FOREIGN_KEY(x) <color:blue>x</color>
!define TABLE(x) entity x << (T,#FFAAAA) >>
!define MANY_TO_MANY(x) entity x << (M,#AAFFAA) >>

hide circle
skinparam linetype ortho

' === ОСНОВНЫЕ СУЩНОСТИ ===
TABLE(Users) {
 PRIMARY_KEY(user_id) : INTEGER \"PK\"
 --
 username : VARCHAR(50)
 email : VARCHAR(100)
 password_hash : TEXT
 created_at : TIMESTAMP
 updated_at : TIMESTAMP
}

TABLE(Decks) {
 PRIMARY_KEY(deck_id) : INTEGER \"PK\"
 --
 name : VARCHAR(100)
 description : TEXT
 FOREIGN_KEY(user_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 is_public : BOOLEAN
 created_at : TIMESTAMP
 updated_at : TIMESTAMP
}

TABLE(Cards) {
 PRIMARY_KEY(card_id) : INTEGER \"PK\"
 --
 FOREIGN_KEY(deck_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 question : TEXT
 answer : TEXT
 explanation : TEXT
 difficulty_level : INTEGER
 created_at : TIMESTAMP
 updated_at : TIMESTAMP
}

TABLE(StudySessions) {
 PRIMARY_KEY(session_id) : INTEGER \"PK\"
 --
 FOREIGN_KEY(user_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 FOREIGN_KEY(deck_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 start_time : TIMESTAMP
 end_time : TIMESTAMP
 cards_studied : INTEGER
 correct_answers : INTEGER
 session_type : VARCHAR(20)
 created_at : TIMESTAMP
}

TABLE(CardReviews) {
 PRIMARY_KEY(review_id) : INTEGER \"PK\"
 --
 FOREIGN_KEY(card_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 FOREIGN_KEY(user_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 rating : VARCHAR(10)
 review_date : TIMESTAMP
 next_review_date : TIMESTAMP
 interval_days : INTEGER
 ease_factor : REAL
 created_at : TIMESTAMP
}

TABLE(MediaFiles) {
 PRIMARY_KEY(media_id) : INTEGER \"PK\"
 --
 FOREIGN_KEY(card_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 file_type : VARCHAR(10)
 file_name : VARCHAR(255)
 file_path : TEXT
 file_size : INTEGER
 mime_type : VARCHAR(100)
 uploaded_at : TIMESTAMP
}

TABLE(Tags) {
 PRIMARY_KEY(tag_id) : INTEGER \"PK\"
 --
 name : VARCHAR(50)
 description : TEXT
 color : VARCHAR(7)
 created_at : TIMESTAMP
}

MANY_TO_MANY(CardTags) {
 FOREIGN_KEY(card_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 FOREIGN_KEY(tag_id) : INTEGER \"FK\"
 --
 assigned_at : TIMESTAMP
}

' === СВЯЗИ МЕЖДУ СУЩНОСТЯМИ ===

' Users - Decks (1:N)
Users ||..o{ Decks : \"creates\"

' Decks - Cards (1:N) 
Decks ||..o{ Cards : \"contains\"

' Users - StudySessions (1:N)
Users ||..o{ StudySessions : \"has\"

' Decks - StudySessions (1:N)
Decks ||..o{ StudySessions : \"studied_in\"

' Cards - CardReviews (1:N)
Cards ||..o{ CardReviews : \"reviewed_in\"

' Users - CardReviews (1:N)
Users ||..o{ CardReviews : \"makes\"

' Cards - MediaFiles (1:N)
Cards ||..o{ MediaFiles : \"has\"

' Cards - Tags (N:M через CardTags)
Cards }o..o{ Tags : \"tagged_with\"
Cards }|--|| CardTags : \"\"
CardTags }|--|| Tags : \"\"

' === ЛЕГЕНДА И ОБОЗНАЧЕНИЯ ===

legend right
 <b>Обозначения:</b>
 -- 
 |**PK**| Первичный ключ |
 |**FK**| Внешний ключ |
 ||..o{| 1:N |
 |}o..o{| N:M |
 |<< (T,#FFAAAA) >>| Таблица |
 |<< (M,#AAFFAA) >>| Таблица связи |
end legend
